Detailed Description

cvmx_npei_int_enb

NPEI_INTERRUPT_ENB = NPI's Interrupt Enable Register

Used to allow the generation of interrupts (MSI/INTA) to the PCIe CoresUsed to enable the various interrupting conditions of NPI
